thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by william

author: william
title: william
text:
The process is great, shopping, shipping and packing.
What is not great is the frame quality, it's obviously inexpensive.
Cheap quality frames, joinery and finishes.
You would think it's Chinese quality, not American.
I only use this supplier due to its convince, until the next delivers a better quality frame.
